{"tid":360840,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求指教 到底點樣鐘意一個人","createTime":"2017-08-15T15:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T16:09:02.000Z","uid":103320,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f79c6a236bbc628e044585a044ae69d042b5bc8","tid":360840,"uid":103320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T15:32:12.000Z","msg":"明明中學時期覺得愛一個人好簡單<br />\n令做每件事都好有動力<br />\n返學可以𥄫佢 見到佢笑都可以令我開心足幾日<br />\n但大左之後就好似唔知咩叫鐘意咩叫愛<br />\n可能出到黎見到世界咁大 咩人都有<br />\n對自己 對對方冇自信<br />\n每每都停留係好感階段就不了了之<br />\n眼見身邊啲朋友個個都搵到另一半<br />\n唔計較咁為對方付出<br />\n都唔好話唔羨慕<br />\n想知當對方係唯一到底係咩感覺<br />\n但偏偏自己就一直搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99df005562e98de6182c0e9b001950e3df28d75","tid":360840,"uid":103320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T15:37:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45a719eb8dbc083038346b0acdebc456eb5d2750","tid":360840,"uid":103320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T15:47:44.000Z","msg":"屌搵人應下我"},{"pid":"e1ebc40b5c60fefbb115be8ec3fb20b9c0a8ac0a","tid":360840,"uid":103320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T15:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81b694836a6f9770bf2696a0c087f202c51eeff","tid":360840,"uid":103320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T15:48:07.000Z","msg":"一推"},{"pid":"811829ec480a7b28ac3c3fdc4196644bd948d291","tid":360840,"uid":103320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T15:48:17.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"1bd190a936988cafe9552060a7ec43012caff172","tid":360840,"uid":103320,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T15:48:30.000Z","msg":"大力推"},{"pid":"03c6b6020b7ff24a9460d60750adbac054c4160f","tid":360840,"uid":953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T15:49:08.000Z","msg":"咪咁啦， 面對現實 做好自己， 遲早預到既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\